list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Setup TemperatureConverter class based on specs
 Constructors which call parent constructors  Overridden convert() method to convert input (Fahrenheit temperature) to Celsius and returns the value. If the instance has no input value, it should return Double.NaN  Use the following formula for conversion: C = ((F-32)*5)/9

task.summary:
